window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The war for control of Haydenâ€™s Knoll begins as a massive army invades the zone. Raytak gathers his forces and marches the legion out to meet the foe. Allies and friends rally to the cause, but will their support be enough to stem the tide? Thousands will clash, and with every swing of his sword and every command given to his army, Raytak is one step closer to remembering those he loves.</p> <p>Can he protect all that he and his friends have built? Will he finally be reunited with his family?</p> <p>Find out in <i>Invasion</i>.</p>"; 
